 \"from\": 457, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"four successive Olympics\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police arrested 47-year-old Windsor man Luke Tones in Brunswick on Wednesday afternoon following a public appeal from police and Ginn.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9695810106166757, \"rank\": 0.03137078337700886, \"text\": \"Luke\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"Brunswick\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday afternoon\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"a public appeal\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"Ginn\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tones has been charged with theft from motor vehicle, obtain property by deception, obtain financial advantage by deception and handle stolen goods.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tones\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"theft\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"motor vehicle\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"property\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"deception\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"financial advantage\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"deception\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"stolen goods\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will face Melbourne Magistrates' Court on November 29.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Magistrates'_Court\", \"score\": 0.9999999953233782, \"rank\": 4.676484108578119e-09, \"text\": \"Melbourne Magistrates' Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Magistrates'_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne_Magistrates'_Court\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Neither the Olympic medals or any of the other allegedly stolen property have been recovered at this time,\\\" a police statement said.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Neither the Olympic medals\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the other allegedly stolen property\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a police statement\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ginn said he had hidden the medals in a secure spot in his car, which was parked on Cumberland Street, after he had shown them at a school event more than a week earlier.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ginn\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"a secure spot\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"his car\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"Cumberland Street\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"a school event\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It must have been about five minutes, it dawned on me that I'd have been at a school event maybe 10 days before ... and then all of a sudden, I was like, 'Oh no',\\\" Ginn told reporters earlier on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about five minutes\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"a school event\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"Ginn\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your heart sinks.\\\"\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your heart\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A wetsuit, a Go Pro camera and headphones were also allegedly stolen, but the rower said it was hard to put a dollar value on the medals.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A wetsuit\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"a Go Pro camera\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"headphones\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"the rower\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"a dollar value\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a hunk of metal - they are gold plated,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hunk\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"metal\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's the reality.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reality\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But for me, it's just it's a horrible feeling to sort of think and imagine that medal will not potentially be in my family.\\\"\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a horrible feeling\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"medal\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Oarsome Foursome was a series of Australian rowing Coxless Four crews, with Ginn taking part in latter combinations which won gold at the Atlanta 1996 Games and silver at London 2012.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9686607241392238, \"rank\": 0.0323491247912334, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coxless_four\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.115094271426619e-49, \"text\": \"Coxless Four\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coxless_four\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coxless_four\"}, {\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.4959190596464595e-12, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Oarsome Foursome\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"Ginn\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"latter combinations\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the Atlanta 1996 Games\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ginn also won gold medals in pair events at Athens 2004 and Beijing 2008.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ginn\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"pair events\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"Athens\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympian has shown his medals to more than 150 schools in the past two decades and hoped he would be able to do so again.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996807674,